Node.Notes: Uncertain. Tree assumes: As for I, span [is] what? The meaning is apparently: Remember that as for me, how long is my life?
Uncertain: Tree assumes: On what account did you create all sons of Adam to be vanity?

Syntax and meaning of infinitival clause uncertain. Tree assumes infinitival clause functions (unusually) like a relative clause: "Remember the reproach of your servants [that] I bear in my heart [from] all the many nations."

(SYNTAX) Clause trees connect ps89:51 and 89:52 together. In verse-based trees, depiction assumes: [Remember the reproach of your servants] with which your enemies mock, with which they mock the steps of your anointed one.
